## Interaction Flow Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["рҹ‘Ҷ Player Touches Screen"] --> B{What was hit?}
    
    B -->|Cat collider| C{Tool Mode?}
    C -->|рҹ–җпёҸ Hand| D["Pet the cat\n(camera zooms in)"]
    C -->|рҹӘ¶ Feather| E["Nothing happens\n(feather doesn't pet)"]
    
    B -->|Bowl collider| F["Fill bowl\n(if empty)"]
    
    B -->|Empty space| G{Tool Mode?}
    G -->|рҹ–җпёҸ Hand + Tap| H["Call cat to spot\n(cat walks over)"]
    G -->|рҹ–җпёҸ Hand + Drag| I["Pan camera\n(horizontal only)"]
    G -->|рҹӘ¶ Feather| J["Move feather toy\n(cat chases it)"]
    
    B -->|Toggle button| K["Switch mode\nрҹ–җпёҸ вҶ” рҹӘ¶"]
```
